OL,3,CChemical castration and early release
OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FSome domestic abusers and sex
OL,8,Foffenders could be released from
OL,9,Fprison early, and chemical castration
OL,10,Fwill be rolled out nationally, under
OL,11,Fnew plans announced by the government.
OL,13,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,14,Fconfirmed on Thursday that the
OL,15,Fgovernment has accepted the majority
OL,16,Fof the recommendations outlined in the
OL,17,Flandmark Independent Sentencing
OL,18,FReview, led by the former justice
OL,19,Fsecretary David Gauke.
