OL,3,CChemical castration and early release
OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FAmong the reforms recommended to free
OL,8,Fup prison spaces is voluntary chemical
OL,9,Fcastration for sex offenders to reduce
OL,10,Freoffending, and releasing criminals
OL,11,Fafter serving just a third of their
OL,12,Fterm if they behave well in jail,
OL,13,Fwhich would include some violent
OL,14,Foffenders.
OL,16,FThe latter measure has already sparked
OL,17,Fbacklash from opposition MPs after the
OL,18,Fgovernment previously insisted violent
OL,19,Fcriminals such as domestic abusers and
OL,20,Fsex offenders would not be eligible
OL,21,Ffor early release.
