OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FThe government is also looking to
OL,8,Fscrap short prison sentences, with
OL,9,FGauke telling ITV News that sentences
OL,10,Funder 12 months do not work and should
OL,11,Fonly be used in exceptional
OL,12,Fcircumstances. He recommends more
OL,13,Foffenders should be managed in the
OL,14,Fcommunity.
