OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FGauke's much-anticipated review was
OL,8,Fcommissioned last year by ministers in
OL,9,Fa bid to ease the overcrowding crisis
OL,10,Fin prisons in England and Wales, when
OL,11,Fit reached such a crisis point that
OL,12,Fthe government had to release
OL,13,Fthousands of inmates early under
OL,14,Femergency measures.
OL,16,FHis report lays bare the dire state of
OL,17,Fthe prison service, projecting that
OL,18,FBritain will have another 9,800
OL,19,Fprisoners by early 2028, which would
OL,20,Flead to chaos in jails that are
OL,21,Falready at bursting point.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
