OL,3,CChemical castration and early release
OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FThe government has accepted reforms to
OL,8,Fallow some criminals, including
OL,9,Fviolent and sexual offenders, to be
OL,10,Freleased at an earlier point in their
OL,11,Fsentence if they show good behaviour.
OL,13,FIn a statement to the Commons on
OL,14,FThursday, the justice secretary
OL,15,Fconfirmed the government has accepted
OL,16,F"in principle" a significant move to
OL,17,Fthree-part sentencing, known as the
OL,18,F"earned progression model".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
