OL,3,CChemical castration and early release
OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FMahmood told MPs: "Under this model,
OL,8,Fan offender will not necessarily leave
OL,9,Fprison at an automatic point. Instead,
OL,10,Ftheir release date will be determined
OL,11,Fby their behaviour.
OL,13,F"If they follow prison rules, they
OL,14,Fwill earn earlier release. If they do
OL,15,Fnot, they will be locked up for
OL,16,Flonger."
OL,18,FThe justice secretary said this
OL,19,Fmeasure echoes a model she has seen in
OL,20,FTexas, "which cut crime and brought
OL,21,Ftheir prison population under control".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
