OL,3,CChemical castration and early release
OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,F"Under this new model, offenders
OL,8,Fserving standard determinate sentences
OL,9,Fwith an automatic release of 40 or 50%
OL,10,Fwill now earn their release," she
OL,11,Fconfirmed.
OL,13,F"The earliest possible release will be
OL,14,Fone third, with additional days added
OL,15,Ffor bad behaviour. The review suggests
OL,16,Fa new maximum of 50%, but for those
OL,17,Fwho behave excessively badly, I will
OL,18,Fnot place an upper limit."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
