OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FTerrorists or the most dangerous
OL,8,Foffenders serving extended sentences
OL,9,Fwould not be eligible for any early
OL,10,Frelease scheme, she added.
OL,12,FThose who are released early based on
OL,13,Fgood behaviour will then undergo a
OL,14,F"period of intensive supervision" in
OL,15,Fthe community, which will see more
OL,16,Foffenders tagged and under close
OL,17,Fmanagement from probation.
OL,19,FHowever, the plans to release some
OL,20,Fviolent criminals early have sparked
OL,21,Fconcern among some.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
