OL,7,FThe domestic abuse commissioner Dame
OL,8,FNicole Jacobs said: "By adopting these
OL,9,Fmeasures government will send a clear
OL,10,Fmessage to domestic abusers that they
OL,11,Fcan offend with little consequence."
OL,13,FCampaign group Justice for Victims
OL,14,Fdescribed the review as not appearing
OL,15,Fto have made a "serious effort" to
OL,16,Funderstand what victims and families
OL,17,Fwant in sentencing policy.
