OL,7,FThe justice secretary said she is
OL,8,F"exploring whether mandating the
OL,9,Fapproach is possible", adding that
OL,10,Fresearch shows the measure can lead to
OL,11,Fa 60% reduction in offending by sex
OL,12,Foffenders.
OL,14,F"Of course, it is vital that this
OL,15,Fapproach is taken alongside
OL,16,Fpsychological interventions that
OL,17,Ftarget other causes of offending, like
OL,18,Fasserting power and control," she
OL,19,Fadded.
