OL,3,CChemical castration and early release
OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FInmates take the drugs alongside
OL,8,Fundergoing psychiatric work that aims
OL,9,Fto tackle other causes of sexual
OL,10,Foffending, such as a desire for power
OL,11,Fand control.
OL,13,FHowever, the review highlighted the
OL,14,Ftreatment would not be relevant for
OL,15,Fsome sex offenders such as rapists who
OL,16,Fare driven by power and control,
OL,17,Frather than sexual preoccupation.
OL,19,FNumerous countries already use this
OL,20,Fapproach to manage sex offenders, such
OL,21,Fas Germany, France, Sweden and Denmark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
