OL,4,Cof some domestic abusers to be
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FIn most countries it is a voluntary
OL,8,Fmeasure, but it is mandatory in some
OL,9,Fcountries and US states.
OL,11,FSuch medications are not currently
OL,12,Fwidely used across prisons in England
OL,13,Fand Wales, and Gauke's report says
OL,14,Fthere is no uniform pathway of
OL,15,Fdelivery of the drugs.
OL,17,FIt was first piloted in 2007 at HMP
OL,18,FWhatton, Nottinghamshire, and was
OL,19,Frolled out to six more prisons in
OL,20,F2016. This was extended in 2022 to
OL,21,Ffive prisons in the south west.
